---
title: Classic Cheeseburger and Cheat's Chicken Caesar Salad with Herby Handcut Chips and Parmigiano Reggiano
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, this tasty Classic Cheeseburger and Cheat's Chicken Caesar Salad is perfect for a casual sharing-style dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R34_W37_UK_SSF16952-3_Main_F1_high-ec80d21f.jpg
